PO2Library.tileworld

Enum TileType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TileType>
      • PO2Library.tileworld.TileType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TileType>, I_Cost, I_RgbColor

    public enum TileType
extends java.lang.Enum<TileType>
implements I_RgbColor, I_Cost
    TileType is an enumeration representing the values a tile can have. Every tile type has its own color and cost.
